{"tid":2437093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母梁震鷹","createTime":"2021-03-07T15:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:07:46.000Z","uid":278351,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b29a50f4c5679331257b907e57935711a7f5dd20","tid":2437093,"uid":278351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"我開post關你撚事咩？<br />\n仆街仔<br />\n搞到我比啲傻仔搞<br />\n令到佢哋成為陰影<br />\n永遠追隨住我<br />\n我就係佢地嘅光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日都係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />梁震英<br />\n班傻仔00後唔識膠文化<br />\n我原諒佢地<br />\n但你咁撚大個人都唔撚化<br />\n將我個postpost上去你嗰度<br />\n有咩政治目的？<br />\n你依家咁得閑<br />\n唔會就係追住我嗰個傻仔呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ebfe37adc161376e84421b55d108ae2444fcd8","tid":2437093,"uid":48631,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FzJ0ERh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzJ0ERh.png&h=c4f410b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQmYrwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQmYrwm.jpg&h=11427bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主係少數理性，懂得反思嘅會員，更獲得梁振英先生嘅讚賞，加油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfxMAqa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfxMAqa.jpg&h=92651f13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"203381e0d96983ef805af5ee0b828e4339ead792","tid":2437093,"uid":278351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2221f1af9fb0511c354e2a9b2610d8a2c4be03","tid":2437093,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得2021年的春天，樓主只係一時衝動？<br />\n<br />\n原本只係想玩下<br />\n估唔到玩到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},